1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,530
Dawn mist above quiet mud houses and empty dirt streets in a small rural village, unfolding quietly.

2
00:00:05,530 --> 00:00:12,560
A barefoot boy in a faded beige shirt stands alone outside a cracked clay house, holding a small cloth bag, unfolding quietly.

3
00:00:12,560 --> 00:00:18,210
Boy walks slowly through dusty village paths as golden morning light falls across his face, unfolding quietly.

4
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:23,969
Old, dry field with cracked earth stretches endlessly under a pale, colorless sky, unfolding quietly.

5
00:00:23,969 --> 00:00:29,710
Boy kneels on hard ground, opens cloth bag, revealing a handful of simple seeds, unfolding quietly.

6
00:00:29,710 --> 00:00:34,780
Boy’s eyes reflect rising sun, filled with quiet determination and belief, unfolding quietly.

7
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,760
Boy digs into dry soil with bare hands, dust coating his skin as the earth resists, unfolding quietly.

8
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:46,550
Boy carefully places a single seed into the ground, covering it with rough, dusty fingers, unfolding quietly.

9
00:00:46,550 --> 00:00:52,270
Boy lifts cracked metal pot and pours water onto the soil, earth absorbs every drop, unfolding quietly.

10
00:00:52,270 --> 00:00:58,560
Dark clouds gather above the field, wind bends dry grass, air grows heavy with anticipation, unfolding quietly.

11
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:04,640
Rain falls softly, then harder. Boy stands still in rain, eyes closed, face lifted, unfolding quietly.

12
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:11,519
After rain, field looks transformed—soft, dark, glistening soil under cloudy sky, alive, unfolding quietly.

13
00:01:11,519 --> 00:01:16,209
Tiny green sprout breaks through wet soil, fragile and full of hope, unfolding quietly.

14
00:01:16,209 --> 00:01:22,579
Boy sits quietly beside the small sprout at sunset, warm light surrounds them, gentle smile, unfolding quietly.

15
00:01:22,579 --> 00:01:28,709
Days pass, skies change, seasons shift as the sprout slowly grows into a small plant, unfolding quietly.

16
00:01:28,709 --> 00:01:34,119
Plant becomes a young tree standing firm in the field, leaves move gently in the wind, unfolding quietly.

17
00:01:34,119 --> 00:01:39,219
Villagers gather nearby, watch the growing tree with curiosity and amazement, unfolding quietly.

18
00:01:39,219 --> 00:01:43,569
Children play and rest in the shade of the tree, laughter fills the air, unfolding quietly.

19
00:01:43,569 --> 00:01:49,489
Years later, older boy stands beside tall tree at golden sunset, looks at it with pride, unfolding quietly.

20
00:01:49,489 --> 00:01:57,149
Village transformed, green fields stretch across land, life returns, tall tree at center under hopeful sky, unfolding quietly.
